snippet.title: Johnny Depp Threatened Amber Heard?!
snippet.description:
Here we are again! In our previous video about recordings exposing Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, I asked you if you thought that they had more evidence that could be released. And we got our answer! At a court hearing in London, some text messages from Johnny to his friend were presented and now the whole situation doesn’t look good for him. Will this new information be in favor of Amber? Does this mean Johnny was the abuser? #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #JamesFranco
